{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName\/notify","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectskeletonsignalname\/notify"]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName.notify","externalID":"s:3GIO28DBusObjectSkeletonSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","symbolKind":"case","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"roleHeading":"Case","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"text":", et al.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}]}]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName":{"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectskeletonsignalname","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName"}],"title":"DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName/notify":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectskeletonsignalname\/notify","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName\/notify","title":"DBusObjectSkeletonSignalName.notify","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]},"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names":{"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","title":"canonical parameter names","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"canonical parameter names","type":"text"}],"url":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"}}}